headline: UBS upgrades Arista Networks on AI infrastructure tailwinds
summary: Investing.com -- UBS upgraded Arista Networks (NYSE:ANET) Inc to "Buy" from "Neutral" and raised its price target to $115 from $112, citing strong data center capital expenditure growth and improving financial metrics.
